{
  "texts": [
    "We initially introduce specific details regarding our setting and then formalize the problem with the following settings:• Unknown Weights: The weights or metrics of the distilled model are not provided.",
    "• Data-free: The original training data is not available, and item statistics (e.g., popularity) are not accessible.",
    "• Unknown Architecture: The training architecture of the distilled safety alignment is also not provided.In general, we have a set of training samples X = {𝑥 1, 𝑥 2,..., 𝑥 𝑁 }.",
    "By querying models, we obtain oracle scores Y = {𝑦 1, 𝑦 2,..., 𝑦 𝑁 }.To enhance performance, we query multiple models.",
    "Considering 𝐾 models, 𝑓 = {𝑓 (1), 𝑓 (2),..., 𝑓 (𝐾) }."
  ]
}